'''剑尾目'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|Xiphosura}}）是[[節肢動物門|節肢動物門]][[肢口綱|肢口綱]]的一目，也是肢口綱現存的唯一一個目，由于整个类群最早出现的时间可回溯至[[奥陶纪|奥陶纪]]，被誉为[[活化石|活化石]]。

==分类==
[[File:Naturkundemuseum_Berlin_-_Mesolimulus_walchi_-_Solnhofen.jpg|thumb]] ''Mesolimulus'']]
剑尾目的分类（{{As of|2018|lc=yes}}）<ref>Dunlop, J. A., Penney, D. & Jekel, D. 2018. [http://www.wsc.nmbe.ch/resources/fossils/Fossils18.5.pdf A summary list of fossil spiders and their relatives] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wsc.nmbe.ch/resources/fossils/Fossils18.5.pdf |date=20180112160024 }}. In World Spider Catalog. Natural History Museum Bern</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Horseshoe crab phylogeny and independent colonizations of fresh water: ecological invasion as a driver for morphological innovation|journal=[[Palaeontology_(journal)|Palaeontology]]|first=James C.|last=Lamsdell|volume=59|issue=2|pages = 181–194|year=2016|doi=10.1111/pala.12220|url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/8c39c23e11df71e5c5247cdd53e7fdb7dc550354}}</ref>:

'''剑尾目 Xiphosura''' <small>Latreille, 1802</small>
*†属 ''Maldybulakia'' <small>Tesakov & Alekseev, 1998 </small> (泥盆纪)
*†属 ''Willwerathia'' <small>Størmer, 1969</small> (泥盆纪)
*†[[卡斯博利鲎科|卡斯博利鲎科]] Kasibelinuridae <small>Pickett, 1993</small> (泥盆纪中期–泥盆纪晚期)
*'''剑尾亚目 Xiphosurida'''
**†[[月盾鲎属|月盾鲎属]] ''Lunataspis'' (奥陶纪晚期)
**†[[博利鲎下目|博利鲎下目]] Bellinurina
***†[[博利鲎科|博利鲎科]] Bellinuridae <small>Zittel & Eastman, 1913</small> (泥盆纪中期–石炭纪晚期)
****†[[博利鲎属|博利鲎属]] ''Bellinurus''
****†属 ''Prestwichia''
****†[[优原穴鲎属|优原穴鲎属]] Euproops (石炭纪)
**[[鲎下目|鲎下目]] Limulina
***†属 ''Bellinuroopsis'' <small>Chernyshev, 1933</small> (石炭纪)
***†[[罗尔夫鲎科|罗尔夫鲎科]] Rolfeiidae <small>Selden & Siveter, 1987</small> (石炭纪早期–二叠纪早期)
***†[[古鲎总科|古鲎总科]] Paleolimuloidea <small>Anderson & Selden, 1997</small>
****†[[古鲎科|古鲎科]] Paleolimulidae <small>Raymond, 1944</small> (石炭纪–二叠纪)
***[[鲎总科|鲎总科]] Limuloidea
****†属 ''Valloisella'' <small>Racheboeuf, 1992</small> (石炭纪)
****†[[澳洲鲎科|澳洲鲎科]] Austrolimulidae <small>Riek, 1955</small> (二叠纪晚期–三叠纪中期)
****[[鲎科|鲎科]] Limulidae <small>Zittel, 1885</small> (三叠纪中期–现代)
*****[[中鱟屬|中鱟屬]] Mesolimulus
*****[[美洲鲎亚科|美洲鲎亚科]] Limulinae <small>Zittel, 1885</small> (侏罗纪晚期–现代)
*****[[东方鲎亚科|东方鲎亚科]] Tachypleinae <small>Pocock, 1902</small> (三叠纪中期–现代)

